g.text: 8. pci_segment, id0, pci segmentpci root, PCI bus
//Constructs a new PCI transport for the given virtio device.
Bus: a BtreeMap that maps address range to BusDevice
read/write on Bus are routed to BusDevice by address
The read/write address on pci_config_mmio BusDevice is decoded into (bus,device,function,register) according
to Pci Express Base Specification 5.0 section 7.2.2 PCI Express Enhanced Configuration Access Mechanism(ECAM)
* one pci device has one interrupt source group
Msi interrupt manager uses HashMap to route irqs
one address allocator for each pci segment
Device inject irq to Guest VM
to trigger VMM forward the packet e.g. via tap
